comment_data.body: It returned to work after changing the linux kernel. It seems that after the update linux-zen did not work well with the flutter. The build froze after a while. The solution was to switch to linux-lts.

@matheust3 Are you still having an issue or is this resolved?

@stevemessick FYI
@kenzieschmoll  It's solved for me. But I don't know if the problem I had is related to the kernel or the flutter
